Alexander Wilkinson owns and maintains the Nail project. Copyright 2025.

It's "open source" to the degree you are doing cool things with it that bring smiles to the people. In that case, you have my blessing to do whatever you want with it - with the exception that you may not commercialize it in any way. 

Should Nail ever become commercially viable, the contributors who helped shape the project will share in its success - to what degree at the sole discretion of Alexander Wilkinson.

This license is perpetual and must be included in all forks, clones, derivations of the code, etc.
